# 🔄 9. DATA PIPELINE

```text
Fetch Data → Process → Aggregate → Store → Serve via API
```

---

## Cron Job:

* Runs every 5–10 minutes
* Updates `wallet_stats` table

---

# 🗄️ 10. DATABASE SCHEMA

## Table: wallet_stats

```sql
wallet_address TEXT
category TEXT
time_range TEXT
wins INT
total_trades INT
win_rate FLOAT
updated_at TIMESTAMP
```

